---
title: Curried Chicken Tortillas with yoghurt and shredded carrot salad
description: The warmed tortillas in this recipe are piled high with some really great ingredients. A subtly spiced curried chicken is complemented with crunchy salad and off topped with a dollop of cooling creamy yoghurt.
